The speaker is saying that when the authors of the 2017 "Attention is All You Need" paper introduced the Transformer architecture, they may not have fully realized how revolutionary it would be for the field of artificial intelligence. The Transformer architecture, which is at the core of the now widely-used language model GPT, changed the way that AI understands and processes language, allowing for the creation of applications like ChatGPT. Despite this monumental impact, the original paper was mostly focused on machine translation.